# Overview of Niama AI

Niama AI is a powerful intelligent assistant built for knowledge, creativity, and problem-solving. It integrates:
- AI tools for communication, creativity, and automation
- Multilingual support (100+ major languages)
- Coding, science, medicine, agriculture, and more

Niama is designed for:
- Researchers
- Students
- Doctors
- Engineers
- Developers
- General users seeking smart assistance

## Goal:
To provide a 24/7 AI companion that can think, respond, and help like a human expert.

# Key Features of Niama AI

- 🧠 Smart AI Brain (multidomain knowledge)
- 🌐 Multilingual Support (100+ languages)
- 💻 Coding & Programming Tools
- 🏥 Medical Advice (non-clinical)
- 🧪 Science & Chemistry Tools
- 🚜 Agriculture Knowledge
- 🏭 Engineering Solutions
- 📸 Camera, Image & Voice input
- 🎙️ Voice Assistant Features
- 💬 Chat Interface
- 🔒 Cloud-based & Secure

# How to Set Up Niama AI (Local Version)

## Requirements
- Python 3.10+
- Node.js
- Git
- Internet

## Steps
1. Clone the repository:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/Modu2018/Niama-ai-website.git

cd Niama-ai-website

cd backend
pip install -r requirements.txt

python app.py


